      <odd id="aspace_c5fb2ed3ed34505bd9bb1684265576bd">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 38-B (YRG 38-B), Records documenting specific sports at Yale.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_4ab266d9c3a95bba2a4cc0a657d3337e">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Department of Athletics, 2005.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_35a9be4f6db554259f6e0d190e066115">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is partially restricted. See Collection Contents for details. Scrapbooks have been microfilmed. Patrons must use HM 184 instead of the originals.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_1c85fd1bf17fb55dd301087316297c30">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
